name: Bike Stunts-Real moto Jump
description:
Bike Stunts-Real moto Jump is easy to pick up but hard to master which will keep you in the zone for hours. Race, jump and make your way through the amazing frontier tracks as you master the skills and the physics of motocross in this high speed stunts adventure. Here is your chance to step up and prove that you are the most intense and competitive biker!motorcycle racing games free..
Features:

- Perform motorbike driving tricks, deadly stunts and obstacle stunts
- Be the crazy moto bike stunt master racer
- Perform your skills on thrilling tracks at full speed
- Amazing game of bike stunts and freestyle racing
- Wonderful amazing latest bike models
- Heavy Bikes and Dirt bikes to perform stunts
- High speed racing with Stunning HD graphics
- Exciting sound effects in action packed game
